OL,3,CUnilever reveals plans to slash 7,500
OL,4,Cjobs and to split from ice-cream
OL,5,Cdivision
OL,7,Fgoods giant Unilever has announced
OL,8,Fplans to spin off its Ben & Jerry's
OL,9,Fice cream division and cut around
OL,10,F7,500 jobs globally as part of a major
OL,11,Fgroup-wide shake-up.
OL,13,FThe firm, which also produces Marmite
OL,14,Fand Dove soap, said the jobs affected
OL,15,Fwould be largely office-based as it
OL,16,Flooks to invest in artificial
OL,17,Fintelligence (AI) and IT to boost
OL,18,Fproductivity and save around 800
OL,19,Fmillion euro (#684 million) over the
OL,20,Fnext three years.
