OL,3,CUnilever reveals plans to slash 7,500
OL,4,Cjobs and to split from ice-cream
OL,5,Cdivision
OL,7,FThe group said staff will be consulted
OL,8,Fabout the cuts, but did not reveal
OL,9,Fwhereabouts they will be made.
OL,11,FThe jobs are expected to go over the
OL,12,Fnext two years.
OL,14,FUnilever has 128,000 employees
OL,15,Fglobally, with 6,000 in the UK.
OL,17,FChief executive Hein Schumacher said:
OL,18,F"Under the growth action plan we have
OL,19,Fcommitted to do fewer things better,
OL,20,Fand with greater impact.
