OL,5,Cdivision
OL,7,F"The changes we are announcing today
OL,8,Fwill help us accelerate that plan."
OL,10,FHe added: "We are committed to
OL,11,Fcarrying out our productivity
OL,12,Fprogramme in consultation with
OL,13,Femployee representatives, and with
OL,14,Frespect and care for those of our
OL,15,Fpeople who are impacted."
OL,17,FThe group's bosses confirmed that AI
OL,18,Fwould "play a role" in the jobs cull
OL,19,Fas part of a "comprehensive" programme
OL,20,Fto invest in technology.
