OL,3,CUnilever reveals plans to slash 7,500
OL,4,Cjobs and to split from ice-cream
OL,5,Cdivision
OL,7,FIt said it was too early to give
OL,8,Fdetails on the types of jobs that
OL,9,Fwould be affected, given the need to
OL,10,Fconsult with staff, but confirmed
OL,11,Froles would go across sites including
OL,12,Fits head office and corporate centres.
OL,14,FUnilever also said the overhaul would
OL,15,Fsee it spin off its ice cream business
OL,16,F- which also includes Wall's and
OL,17,FMagnum brands - most likely through a
OL,18,Fseparate stock market listing.
