OL,5,Cdivision
OL,7,FIt has not yet decided whether the ice
OL,8,Fcream arm would be listed in London or
OL,9,Fthe Netherlands, where the division is
OL,10,Fcurrently headquartered.
OL,12,FThe ice cream division delivered
OL,13,Fturnover of 7.9 billion euro (#6.8
OL,14,Fbillion) last year, but Unilever said
OL,15,Fit differed from the rest of the group
OL,16,Fdue to its seasonal sales nature,
OL,17,Fwhile it also has a frozen supply
OL,18,Fchain and "high capital requirements".
